query:
-- Dados da gestante
SELECT 
  g.id,
  g.nome,
  g.email,
  g.telefone,
  g.dataNascimento,
  g.dum,
  g.dataUltrassom,
  g.igUltrassomSemanas,
  g.igUltrassomDias,
  g.altura,
  g.pesoInicial,
  g.gesta,
  g.para,
  g.tipoPartoDesejado,
  m.nome as medico,
  ps.nome as planoSaude,
  (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM consultasPrenatal WHERE gestanteId = g.id) as total_consultas,
  (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM resultadosExames WHERE gestanteId = g.id) as total_exames,
  (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM ultrassons WHERE gestanteId = g.id) as total_ultrassons
FROM gestantes g
LEFT JOIN medicos m ON g.medicoId = m.id
LEFT JOIN planosSaude ps ON g.planoSaudeId = ps.id
WHERE g.nome = 'TESTE - Gestante Exemplo';
